subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous fort is located in Jodhpur?
question_hi: जोधपुर में किस मंगल पर्वत है?
explanation_en: Umaid Bhawan Palace is a famous fort located in Jodhpur. Mehrangarh Fort and Khejarli are other notable forts in Rajasthan, while Rajasthan Renaissance is a movement and Umaid Bhawan Palace is a palace, not a fort.
explanation_hi: उमाई बहान पल्किल जोड़ाई मैंज़ाई एक राजस्थान में आवश्यका एक पैल्याई है, जोड़ाई एक राजस्थानी मैंज़ाई है, जोड़ाई एक पैल्याई है। केहूँ जोड़ाई एक राजस्थानी है, ।
explanation_en: Umaid Bhawan Palace is the largest private residence in the world and is located in Jodhpur. Khejarli is a historical site related to the Marwar region of Rajasthan, not a fort. Mehrangarh Fort is a famous fort in Jodhpur.
